Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换句话说就是硬着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:46.72,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（硬着陆）
